document_data.History:
Cedric assumed the throne in the {{YearlinkName|1207}}, after the death of King Adrian.

In [[1228 DR|the twenty-first year of his reign]], much of the [[Korinn Archipelago]] was conquered by [[Viledel]].{{Cite dragon/362/Grand History of the Realms: The Moonshaes|30}}

Cedric ruled for thirty-six years before he died of natural causes in the {{YearlinkName|1243}}.
